docs {
  # A2A Multi-Agent Demo (Bruno)

  This collection validates a 3-agent A2A flow:
  - Register coordinator/planner/validator agents in a2a-registry using `cardUrl`
  - Verify discovery via `/.well-known/agents/index.json`
  - Invoke `/invoke` on each agent endpoint and track task ids

  Endpoint target assumptions:
  - registry uses `POST /agents` (authenticated listing/index still uses token auth in this repo)
  - agents expose A2A JSON-RPC at `<agentBaseUrl>/invoke`
  - run steps should be executed in numeric order

  Suggested run order:
  1. Registry Health
  2. Publish Coordinator Agent
  3. Publish Planner Agent
  4. Publish Validator Agent
  5. Registry List Agents
  6. Registry Discovery Index
  7. Invoke Coordinator + Poll
  8. Invoke Planner + Poll
  9. Invoke Validator + Poll
}
